data.description: Welcome to your dream home, just minutes from the beach! This stunning property boasts a large open floorplan, perfect for entertaining and everyday living. The spacious kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring gorgeous granite countertops, plentiful cabinet space and a large center island, perfect for meal prep and gatherings. Expand your entertaining to the lovely dining room that features beautiful wainscoting. Relax in the expansive living room that includes a charming fireplace for those chilly nights or retreat to the primary bedroom completed with two walk-in closets and an ensuite bath featuring both a shower and a soaking tub. 3 additional large bedrooms and a second full bathroom with double vanity occupy the second floor. This home also offers a convenient two-car garage with fantastic storage space and a large, fenced-in backyard, ideal for outdoor activities. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
